# CUSTOM .GITIGNORE FOR MULTIMEDIA ARCHIVES
# ====================================================================

# --- OS Trash & System Cache ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Icon?

# --- Gigantic Raw Audio & Video Formats (Prevents GitHub Sync Crashes) ---
# Uncompressed raw master files belong on external clouds, not GitHub.
*.wav
*.aiff
*.caf
*.raw
*.mov
*.mkv
*.avi

# --- Allowed Media Formats (Compressed & Safe for Git Storage) ---
# Git handles these well if kept under 50MB per file.
!*.mp3
!*.flac
!*.ogg
!*.mp4
!*.webm
!*.midi
!*.mid

# --- Digital Audio Workstation (DAW) & Video Editing Project Dumps ---
# Ignore massive autosave cache folders from production software.
*.als         # Ableton Live
*.logic       # Logic Pro
*.cpr         # Cubase
*.flp         # FL Studio
*.prproj      # Adobe Premiere
*.drp         # DaVinci Resolve
.render_cache/
